body.p:
The agent can be installed on the following operating systems:


Windows (from 2000 up to 7, including the Windows Server editions), 32 and 64 bits;

Linux-based systems;

FreeBSD, OpenBSD, NetBSD, DragonFlyBSD;

Mac OS X from 10.3.9 (PowerPC processors) to 10.6 (Intel processors);

Solaris, OpenSolaris, OpenIndiana (SPARC and Intel);

AIX;

HP-UX (Pa-RISC and IA64).
